com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.components

Class GSpinnerNumberModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.AbstractSpinnerModel
      • javax.swing.SpinnerNumberModel
        • com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.components.GSpinnerNumberModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SpinnerModel

    public class GSpinnerNumberModel
extends SpinnerNumberModel
implements Serializable
    Just like SpinnerNumberModel but allow reaching the maximum/minimum using up/down controls, rather than stopping at the value before the maximum/minimum

    e.g. if the step size is 10, and the current value is 5 less than the maximum, pressing up in a standard SpinnerNumberModel will do nothing, but this implementation will change the value to be the maximum.

    See Also:
